    Overview

  • Command prefix

    Default: , or @mention

    Example: , help or @loser help

  • Command usage syntax

    : means that the argument is required

    [argument]: means that the argument is optional

    <"thing1" | "thing2">: means that you need to select one of these options

  • setjail strict

    Module

    Settings

    Aliases

    removeroles

    Description

    Toogle strict jail system.

Strict jail removes **all** roles that user had except the jail role and restores them after user is unjailed.

    Usage

    @loser setjail strict

  • autoresponders

    Module

    Settings

    Aliases

    responses, ar, autoresponder

    Description

    Create custom autoresponses

`*word*` - every message containing word.
`word*` - every message that starts with word.
`*word` - every message that ends with word.
`word` - every message that equals word.

    Usage

    @loser autoresponders

  • purge

    Module

    Moderator

    Aliases

    remove, clear, c

    Description

    `--user`: A mention or name of the user to remove.
`--contains`: A substring to search for in the message.
`--starts`: A substring to search if the message starts with.
`--ends`: A substring to search if the message ends with.
`--after`: Messages must come after this message ID.
`--before`: Messages must come before this message ID.
`--bot`: Check if it's a bot user.
`--embeds`: Check if the message has embeds.
`--files`: Check if the message has attachments.
`--emoji`: Check if the message has custom emoji.
`--reactions`: Check if the message has reactions
`--or`: Use logical OR for all options.
`--not`: Use logical NOT for all options.

    Usage

    @loser purge  [arguments]

  • purge

    Module

    Moderator

    Aliases

    remove, clear, c

    Description

    `--user`: A mention or name of the user to remove.
`--contains`: A substring to search for in the message.
`--starts`: A substring to search if the message starts with.
`--ends`: A substring to search if the message ends with.
`--after`: Messages must come after this message ID.
`--before`: Messages must come before this message ID.
`--bot`: Check if it's a bot user.
`--embeds`: Check if the message has embeds.
`--files`: Check if the message has attachments.
`--emoji`: Check if the message has custom emoji.
`--reactions`: Check if the message has reactions
`--or`: Use logical OR for all options.
`--not`: Use logical NOT for all options.

    Usage

    @loser purge  [arguments]

    {boostlevel} -> boosts level
    {last} -> last joined user
    {last.name} -> last joined user name
    {last.tag} -> last joined user tag
    {last.id} -> last joined user id

    Usage

    @loser serverstats add
